                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Varius <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Pup</abbr><ex>inia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XLV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXIIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Varius Sabinus <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ietate</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die letzte Zeile erlaubt mehrere Auflösungen: f(ecit) p(ro) p(ietate); f(ratri) p(ro) p(ietate); f(ilius) p(ro) p(ietate); f(ilius) p(atri) p(osuit). In Bogennische oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Brustbild eines bartlosen Mannes in toga. (B): Z. 5: f(ratri) p(ro) p(ietate). (B): AE 1978: Z. 4: XXIII.</p>
            </div>
